schools.name: Byron P Steele Ii High School

data.description: This beautiful home is located in a wonderful area with easy access to grocery stores, restaurants and great schools along with a new EVO Entertainment Center. The kitchen has granite countertops, island, breakfast bar & spacious floor plan that opens to a cozy family room. Great for family & friend gatherings! Large Master, bath & closet. The 4th bedroom can be used as an office space, gym, or your very own mini movie theater. It has awesome neighborhood amenities like a basketball & volleyball court, huge clubhouse, and a pool for everyone to enjoy.
